data.text: Hmmm... I can't blink through that. There's no telling what's on the other side.
Or are you too cowardly to face my cold steel?
YOU THERE! Who are you? Tell me now.
I'm... err... Ryder... Who are you?
I am Sir Jacob, a trusted member of the King's Royal Guard, and I am on a mission.
Say... young traveller, have you seen a wizard among these parts?
I chased him to the opening of the cave. He seems to have brought us here by some dark magic.
Yeah! I think I saw him too, just outside.
It is my duty to find him. I will knock him to the ground. Are you experienced with that dagger?
I'll be watching you... fellow wanderer.
WHAT! You blinked! You're a wizard?
Well as long as you're on the side of good deeds then we shall have no quarrel.
